column14: something that can be directed at arbitrary things
something that can fly and treat most objects as surfaces in relatively good taste
something that can be loved generically and in good taste
beaten in good taste and makes noise
something that motivates and alters men in good taste
capable of virtually everything that requires agency and sapience
something that is exchanged and has value
eats men in relatively (fanciful) good taste
carried by men, hit or thrown in good taste
passes through most objects, without or without interiors
drunk, swum in, cools most objects
closed, opened, and broken in good taste
